Implements device control/telemetry API with simple header-based auth,
SQLAlchemy models (devices, device_state, telemetry), an MQTT publisher
for relay commands, an MQTT consumer service that persists state and
telemetry from ESP32 devices, plus Docker/Compose setup with Mosquitto
and Postgres.

